Metadata: Washington Sea Grant Program 2001-2004, Research, Outreach and Partnerships
University of Washington Sea Grant Program
program reports (annual, progress, planning reports, etc)

This booklet describes Washington Sea Grant Program's current and future activities. Over fifty projects and programs are documented here, and fall within the following categories: marine advisory services, communications, Northwest programs, living marine resources, ecosystem health, new technologies, economic and community development, education and training, and fellowships.
